        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 8. Light microscopic photographs and line drawings of Hornestheria? Morphotype 1 from Punta Negra 2 site; uppermost part of Unit C, lower Anisian. A–B, compacted carapace in lateral view (DA21/03/04/11). C–D, external view on a right carapace valve (DA21/03/04/07-1a). E–F, internal side of a right carapace valve, appearing optically inverted through artificial shallow-angle illumination (DA21/03/04/07-2a)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4715228/files/figure.png" .

