<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4715269>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 11. A–B, light microscopic photograph and line drawing of external view on a right carapace valve (DA21/03/04/09), showing the positions of the ESEM images. C–D, ESEM images of Hornestheria? Morphotype 2 from Punta Negra 2 site; uppermost part of Unit C, lower Anisian; irregularly (not smoothly) preserved surface, the ornamentation is not clearly detectable even under high magnification." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4715269/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4715253>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 10. Light microscopic photographs and line drawings of Hornestheria? Morphotype 2 from Punta Negra 2 site, showing more or less developed concave bending of the ventral margin in the median-posterior area of the carapace valve; uppermost part of Unit C, lower Anisian. A–B, Right carapace valve, almost completely preserved as a steinkern (DA21/03/04/07-1b). C–D, imprint of a right carapace valve, appearing optically inverted through shallow illumination (DA21/03/04/07-2b). E–F, external side of a left carapace valve, overlying the internal side of the corresponding right carapace valve; both carapace valves are shifted relative to each other (DA21/03/04/08)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4715253/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4715242>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 9. Light microscopic photographs and line drawings of Hornestheria? Morphotype 1 from Punta Negra 2 site; uppermost part of Unit C, lower Anisian. A–B, compacted carapace in lateral view; rock surface was covered with adhesive (DA21/03/04/07-1d). C–D, external side of a left carapace valve (DA21/03/04/12-1). E–F, external side of a fragmented right carapace valve (DA21/03/04/13a)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4715242/files/figure.png" .
